headline: Industry First: Regions Bank Launches Convenient, Seamless Digital Portal for Real Estate Banking Clients
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., September 15, 2025--Regions Bank on Monday announced the launch of a digital borrower portal designed to make banking easier and more convenient for Real Estate Banking clients with construction projects underway.
